# Example environment configuration. Copy to `.env.local` for local development.
# `.env.local` is gitignored — never commit real secrets.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# League password gate (per-league privacy bridge — see LEAGUE-PRIVACY-PASSWORD)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Required whenever any league has a password set. The signing logic uses this
# value (HMAC-SHA256) to mint and verify the `league_auth_<slug>` session
# cookie. Generate a long random value:
#
#   openssl rand -hex 32
#
# Do NOT use a short or human-memorable value. There is no in-code default —
# the gate logic throws on missing/empty to fail loud.
LEAGUE_AUTH_SECRET=

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cron authentication (scheduled jobs in vercel.json)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Bearer token the scheduled cron routes require: /api/cron/season-transition,
# /api/cron/season-rollover, /api/cron/game-stats. The routes fail closed — a
# missing/unset value makes every scheduled run return 401, silently disabling
# automated season transition, rollover, and weekly game-stats ingestion.
# Generate a long random value:
#
#   openssl rand -hex 32
CRON_SECRET=
